526	  report.step(
527	    'Act VIII — 15 concurrent signed webhooks; none silently dropped; the shop stays responsive',
528	    'fifteen independently-signed demo webhooks fired at once are all accepted (coalescing OK, loss not); an ordinary THING turn right after still completes',
